{"tid":1429773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想同大家講講之後既運動發展","createTime":"2019-08-07T14:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T15:41:39.000Z","uid":69696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a1296402ea02e1c210bb2e1f7620c78d363332e1","tid":1429773,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:46:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>1．對執法失去信心既後果 </ins></strong><br />\n起底及大量網上批評係對狗完全失去信心既表現。最怕係有人<span style=\"color: red;\">別有用心</span>，為一己私利<span style=\"color: red;\">去報復唔關事既人</span>，呢類人係極度難防。  <br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>2．無政府主義 </ins></strong><br />\n每一次既<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武對抗</span>，會令該地<span style=\"color: red;\">短暫脫離政府控制</span>。我對各位無名抗爭者既自制力有絕對信心，<span style=\"color: red;\">但無政府狀態會好易引誘壞人趁火打劫</span>，尤其當<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武對抗變得頻繁，會令人習慣同唔怕冒險犯罪</span>。 <br />\n切記<span style=\"color: red;\">只要有一單打劫，都會令運動蒙上污點</span>。  <br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>3．經濟抗爭 </ins></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">只有經濟抗爭先對共產黨有實質打擊</span>： <br />\na. 拋售含港中股票及債卷既強積金 <br />\nb. 取消中資定期、保險及戶口 <br />\nc. 拋港紙，將資產轉外幣放係離岸戶口 <br />\nd. 拋售港中資股票 <br />\ne. 製造消息 ，指貿易戰底下中國會輸，香港資產唔再穩定，呼籲其他人投資其他國家  <br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>4．擴大和理非模式 </ins></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆必需繼續</span>，並繼續以<span style=\"color: red;\">其他藝術方式如塗鴉、微電影、短片、畫、漫畫、音樂</span>等等延續運動。"},{"pid":"ce93226c0434f99319f04567ce79459daa6a5fea","tid":1429773,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f986e576719adebff58487635cc2059ac71b3b","tid":1429773,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:50:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9ef371dc3449d25b2d81a3fbe6d2880adc8d67","tid":1429773,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:53:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9717b1d58df082861917a11b22f9debdacf72a6e","tid":1429773,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:03:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e7dac273e97343a967252783a59aaca49bbb51","tid":1429773,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:33:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ff015cb2a9f11efe2a138f3645a2addc219905","tid":1429773,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}